data.description: Two-story, 2700SF+, 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in Midtown Longview! As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting atmosphere, complete with two spacious living areas, one currently being used as a 5th bedroom, providing ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. The updated kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances, gas range, granite countertops, and a captivating wood accent ceiling that adds warmth and character to the space. The practicality of daily living is seamlessly integrated with a large laundry/pantry area, ensuring organization and efficiency along with a downstairs half bath. New, vinyl plank flooring throughout adds durability and contemporary flair, while a cozy gas fireplace and built-ins invite cozy evenings during colder months. Outdoor enthusiasts will rejoice in the expansive backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying some fresh air. A convenient mudroom and back gate additional entrance enhance the functionality of the property, while a one-car carport provides shelter for your vehicle. With its modern amenities, spacious layout, and prime location in Midtown Longview, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication.
